40:04.220 --> 40:05.960
<i>Vamos, mi amor.</i>

40:34.720 --> 40:36.150
Thank you.

40:38.150 --> 40:39.620
Honey told me
you lost your family.

40:41.620 --> 40:42.730
I lost mine too.

40:46.730 --> 40:47.780
No talk of family.

41:32.780 --> 41:34.440
They're here, boys!

41:34.440 --> 41:36.350
The girls are here!

41:45.260 --> 41:46.260
Hello, lads!

41:49.230 --> 41:51.360
Whoo!

42:05.310 --> 42:06.750
What you got there?
I'll take it all.

42:25.270 --> 42:26.270
Hello!

42:55.860 --> 42:57.670
My cases are in there, love.

42:57.670 --> 42:59.430
How are we?

42:59.430 --> 43:02.100
Nice to see you all.
Have you had a bath?

43:03.100 --> 43:05.240
Oh, then you might
need another one!

43:05.240 --> 43:07.670
Bertie!
They're here!

43:07.680 --> 43:08.840
The lasses are here!

43:20.590 --> 43:22.190
Well, ladies, ladies, ladies.

43:22.190 --> 43:24.190
Welcome, welcome.

43:25.200 --> 43:26.630
Well, well, well.

43:26.630 --> 43:28.430
What a divine selection.

43:28.430 --> 43:31.170
I'm Bertie Russell.
At your attendance.

43:31.170 --> 43:32.870
I trust your journey
treated you well?

43:32.870 --> 43:34.570
No. It was shit.

43:34.570 --> 43:36.710
Oh, well, uh...

43:36.710 --> 43:39.710
Let's hope that your stay with us
proves to be just the opposite.

43:39.710 --> 43:41.380
Delightful, in fact.

43:41.380 --> 43:43.410
And fruitful to us all.

43:44.410 --> 43:46.880
Uh, Mr. McCullen has a
meeting at West Port,

43:46.890 --> 43:51.520
so it's my honorable duty
to escort you to...

43:52.520 --> 43:53.800
well, your boudoirs.

44:00.800 --> 44:03.400
Ah, an English rose.
I like it.

44:03.400 --> 44:05.570
You're gonna go down a treat.

44:05.570 --> 44:07.200
All right, gentlemen.

44:07.210 --> 44:08.570
Give the ladies time
to freshen up,

44:08.570 --> 44:11.750
and after that, you can throw all
your money and yourselves at them.

44:13.740 --> 44:18.350
Soon all this will be out of here, and
we'll have more rooms for more girlies.

44:18.350 --> 44:19.620
This is just the beginning.

44:19.620 --> 44:21.590
Look at that stage, ladies.

44:21.590 --> 44:23.520
Drapes will make it nice.

44:23.520 --> 44:24.590
Aye.

44:24.590 --> 44:26.620
A touch of class.

44:26.620 --> 44:29.390
Now where's the English rose?
Ah, there you are.

